{"tid":2033253,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"香港獨立唯一出路？想問香港人真的有這個懶趴嘛？","createTime":"2020-05-24T14:05:27.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-24T15:02:38.000Z","uid":52658,"like":5,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"00e1dda122c4c9b29a9408381038822c45703392","tid":2033253,"uid":52658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T14:05:27.000Z","msg":"剛聽到蠻多人在喊這句<br />\n<br />\n先說明一下 我支持你們獨立<br />\n但先不談香港獨立的可能性<br />\n但都是一個很芭樂的問題 香港沒有軍隊<br />\n如果香港獨立後就要參軍 你們會願意？<br />\n有多少人會願意？<br />\n而且香港太靠近大陸 要面對的威脅是十倍於台灣<br />\n除了軍事威脅以外<br />\n中國亦會用不同的方法打壓你們<br />\n像是斷水啊 封鎖海陸邊境啊 經濟制裁啊<br />\n什麼什麼洨的<br />\n獨立了以後很有可能變成中國的傀儡國<br />\n結果可能跟現在沒什麼分別<br />\n你們又484會接受？<br />\n<br />\n所以我倒是覺得啦<br />\n以上的問題你們解決掉 才有資格談獨立<br />\n現在還不是時機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b0e7b1bab2c9c22452953c9b5a5dee3c262d156a","tid":2033253,"uid":79793,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T14:07:23.000Z","msg":"好多國家都冇軍隊咖啦"},{"pid":"c6705ce9eb38442023b41277693a28e498556bf4","tid":2033253,"uid":229296,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T14:09:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />水同參軍問題其實係講得幾好<br />\n多人肯參都好，近成咁打起上黎點夠做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但唔獨立有咩機會搞水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"00ac5ed0ea475bf6fc8298ce1320c7c9941eaf31","tid":2033253,"uid":256914,"like":2,"dislike":4,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T14:11:11.000Z","msg":"有錢 請美軍 <br />\n海水化淡平過買支那水<br />\n入口貨品有一半以唔係支那既"},{"pid":"c28dd2e24401b49b96e9d1c72cf8f2bde338eee9","tid":2033253,"uid":46309,"like":16,"dislike":1,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T14:12:48.000Z","msg":"妳不會具備所有條件才會想做一件事；<br />\n妳是想做一件事，然後慢慢克服所有條件。<br />\n<br />\n就如妳不會先儲錢才想到買想要的東西，<br />\n而是有想要的東西，才想方設法儲錢。<br />\n<br />\n我想買東西，你當刻問我有沒有錢，我覺得有錢沒錢關你屁事？我不能有想的念頭？"},{"pid":"d156b04a43861cb62b3dfd8f46bc7e048f3be64f","tid":2033253,"uid":13327,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T14:13:35.000Z","msg":"2樓有講  世界上  好多國家都係無軍隊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有國家比錢請人做防衛<br />\n有國家同隔離國家合作協防  等等等等..."},{"pid":"0f30e6ae880a6cef371b5da2fd48aa64e0a4b519","tid":2033253,"uid":168400,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T14:15:30.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"21c494a78eea26160b6761fc638faf0c9e8cbe93","tid":2033253,"uid":138609,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T14:17:19.000Z","msg":"地理上其實有樣好不利<br />\n香港南面西南面有珠海控制既萬山群島<br />\n東北面有深圳控制既大鵬半島<br />\n換言之香港得東南面可以出到國際水域<br />\n呢一點其實好不利 但之前好似無人講過"},{"pid":"adf0bd52095cb766f93488992105374641186859","tid":2033253,"uid":210755,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T14:18:22.000Z","msg":"獨立，除左支共解體外 無任何辨法, 支爆倒台 再由老美託管  先獨立調查+重組警隊，大規模抽出犯罪黑警, 由警隊基礎上 內外招募擔任國防任務 &amp; join同盟"},{"pid":"a49ba60eb279aefbc208afd461c7f1ebae220a27","tid":2033253,"uid":93986,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T14:19:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pccMsVY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpccMsVY.jpg&h=18a7b597&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8a786ff7613dd264723b09b09d37e34b93500fac","tid":2033253,"uid":333488,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T14:20:14.000Z","msg":"冇軍隊嘅國家等於不設防任人魚肉"},{"pid":"897d43ca311130d7445019ae2bd47f42801de240","tid":2033253,"uid":52658,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T14:24:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d5f45ec2b394ce1a7bcad48d7af0d319db2aeb9d","tid":2033253,"uid":247471,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T14:26:03.000Z","msg":"軍隊立國時就可以training ，最重要係立法先"},{"pid":"ceb79585ae6f7ce480cf75c8d72f8af01f63c098","tid":2033253,"uid":358604,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"8a786ff7613dd264723b09b09d37e34b93500fac","tid":2033253,"uid":333488,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T14:20:14.000Z","msg":"冇軍隊嘅國家等於不設防任人魚肉"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T14:31:49.000Z","msg":"地理位置先係重點"},{"pid":"d2ae54bf87835c7f095d067113859305a607abc8","tid":2033253,"uid":304845,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T14:37:23.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7b5dc8c92af6f74af0c9fac837d08ee7ad06fbd0","tid":2033253,"uid":52658,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T14:59:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c7eaffcf2fa415762917e29a5506d6b0409a914","tid":2033253,"uid":30791,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T15:00:12.000Z","msg":"香港獨立同中共既存在基本上係一個矛盾"},{"pid":"d241e9c24c141c1f322ba60a5778c5ba8e97ef32","tid":2033253,"uid":30791,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"7c7eaffcf2fa415762917e29a5506d6b0409a914","tid":2033253,"uid":30791,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T15:00:12.000Z","msg":"香港獨立同中共既存在基本上係一個矛盾"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T15:02:38.000Z","msg":"香港獨立的可能性 應該細過中共倒台既可能性<br />\n然而幾個人既然起來 你不能說決沒有毀壞這鐵屋的希望。"}]}